            <caption>Figure 7. 6x4 Tractor With Full Vehicle Control Antilock Brake System</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1>1. M21 MODULATOR</callout1>
                <callout1>2. WHEEL SPEED SENSORS</callout1>
                <callout1>3. MODULAR (PUSH-PULL) CONTROL VALVE</callout1>
